OL,3,CHard-working Scots left squealing from
OL,4,CSNP's high taxes, says Sir Tom Hunter
OL,6,FIn his Entrepreneurs Manifesto for
OL,7,FScotland, he claimed 100,000 jobs
OL,8,Fcould be created and #20.2 billion
OL,9,Fadded to the economy by stripping back
OL,10,Fregulation, cutting taxes and axing
OL,11,Fquangos, among other measures to make
OL,12,Fdoing business easier and unlock
OL,13,Fopportunities in energy.
OL,15,FAsked if Scotland is too prone to
OL,16,Ftaxing, he said: "I think that's it.
OL,17,FThe answer is, 'Oh, we don't have
OL,18,Fenough money, we'll just tax people
OL,19,Fmore'.
