OL,3,CHard-working Scots left squealing from
OL,4,CSNP's high taxes, says Sir Tom Hunter
OL,6,F"I think we are overtaxed in Scotland
OL,7,Fand people are now squealing.
OL,9,F"I'm certainly squealing. Not because
OL,10,Fof my personal income tax, I'll always
OL,11,Fpay my income tax in Scotland, and
OL,12,FI'll go with it.
OL,14,F"But the general population now, the
OL,15,Fhard-working people, are being
OL,16,Fovertaxed."
OL,18,FSir Tom said he wants to see a "fairer
OL,19,Fsystem" "so that the tax take goes up,
OL,20,Fnot the tax rate".
