OL,3,CHard-working Scots left squealing from
OL,4,CSNP's high taxes, says Sir Tom Hunter
OL,6,F"This is nurses, teachers and
OL,7,Fpolicemen. I wouldn't call these
OL,8,Fpeople particularly wealthy but
OL,9,Fthey're paying half of their income
