OL,4,CSNP's high taxes, says Sir Tom Hunter
OL,6,F"Well look, the way to get
OL,7,Findependence is through competent
OL,8,Fgovernment.
OL,10,F"If the Government had made a success
OL,11,Fof the powers they have, then you'd be
OL,12,Fin a strong position to say, 'let's go
OL,13,Ffurther'.
OL,15,F"But our economy is lacklustre and our
OL,16,Feducation system is falling down in
OL,17,Fthe rankings.
OL,19,F"So we haven't made the most of the
